  </div>

  <!-- Mid-page CTA -->
  <div class="bg-gold/10 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-xl p-5 my-8 not-prose">
    <p class="font-bold text-navy text-base mb-1">Need an Alfa Laval MOPX 209 or Spare Parts?</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-light mb-3">Dolphin Centrifuge supplies remanufactured MOPX 209 centrifuges and the complete DMPX-042 system module — with heaters, pump, PLC controls, and full warranty. Parts for all MOPX models in stock.</p>
    <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="inline-block bg-gold text-white font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gold/90 transition-colors">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
  </div>
<!-- Bottom CTA Bar -->
  <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-6 mt-10 not-prose text-center">
    <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-2">Ready to Source Alfa Laval MOPX 209 Parts or a Remanufactured Unit?</p>
    <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mb-4">Call Dolphin Centrifuge at <a href="tel:+12485222573" class="text-gold font-semibold">(248) 522-2573</a> or request a quote online.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
      <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="bg-gold text-white font-semibold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-gold/90 transition-colors text-sm">Get a Quote</a>
      <a href="/industrial-centrifuge-sample-testing/" class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/30 font-semibold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors text-sm">Sample Testing</a>
